reviewText: Best season of Baywatch. I have now watching Baywatch Nights since the Baywatch series is so addicting.
Of the nine seasons of Baywatch 7 is definitely one of the best. Probably the best cast lineup and stronger storylines .
Love the purchases right on time
The DVDs in this collection do not seem to have the sharpness of the original older version.
Love the storylines and all the beautiful scenery.
